Saudi-Led Coalition Declares Five-Day Humanitarian Truce in Yemen
A Saudi-led military coalition Saturday announced a five-day humanitarian cease-fire in Yemen, where it has been carrying out a campaign of airstrikes against the countryâ€™s Iran-backed Houthi rebels since March.
